  "description": "The ∞ symbol IS a figure-eight. Here, very high entrainment (0.9) locks the 6 Kuramoto oscillators into near-unison at a very slow 0.18 Hz — the whole figure-eight breathes as one. Tangle at 0.6 keeps the topology active but entrainment smooths all variation into a single unified breath. Meditative.",
